{"type": "article", "id": 9507, "title": "Filson 防水包袋", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-13T07:37:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235018eHw7BOQMcbVJ3h5v.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t美国户外品牌 Filson 发布了一个名为 “Green” 的防水包袋系列，整体以军绿色为主色调，包含有不同尺寸的背包，旅行包等六个款式，材料上采用的是聚酯纤维，上面有乙烯基涂层，防水耐用。不管在什么环境下，这款包包都是防水的给力帮手。这个系列价格在 35 美元到 200 美元之间，<a href=\"http://www.filson.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235016jr70PRKqMnv2QTla.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.13839286\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235016la35eXxNvDcJPRbY.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.51388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235017Jj1eWw02KrgCQxT8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.77592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235017BGfH8gVwmIMkUlN2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.87962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}